{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "8c0f0f3a-b3f2-4f55-8c6c-9e59682651e2",
    "name": "API Documentation Online Shop Adhivasindo",
    "description": "# API Documentation — Online Shop Adhivasindo\n\nThis collection contains all API endpoints for the **Online Shop Adhivasindo** platform — a RESTful API for managing an online shop including authentication, products, product types, and orders.\n\n## Base URL\n\nAll requests use the `{{apiUrl}}` environment variable as the base URL. Make sure the **Online Shop Adhivasindo** environment is selected before sending requests.\n\n## Authentication\n\nMost endpoints require a **Bearer Token**. Use the **Login** or **Register** endpoint to obtain a token. The token is automatically saved to the `{{token}}` environment variable by the test scripts.\n\n## Environment Variables\n\n| Variable | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `apiUrl` | Base URL of the API server |\n| `token` | Bearer access token (auto-set on login/register/refresh) |\n| `type_id` | ID of the last created/updated product type |\n| `product_id` | ID of the last created product |\n| `product_id_active` | ID of an active product (auto-mapped from Get All Products) |\n| `product_id_inactive` | ID of an inactive product |\n| `product_id_out_of_stock` | ID of an out-of-stock product |\n| `product_id_draft` | ID of a draft product |\n| `product_id_low_stock` | ID of a low-stock product |\n| `order_id` | ID of the last created order |\n\n## Folder Structure\n\n| Folder | Description |\n|---|---|\n| **Config** | Health check and server status |\n| **Authentication** | Register, login, logout, token refresh, and user profile |\n| **Products** | Full CRUD for products |\n| **Product Types** | Full CRUD for product categories |\n| **Orders** | Checkout, order listing, and order status management |",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "29572339"
  },
