            "description": "Updates an existing product by its ID. Uses method spoofing via the `_method: PATCH` field since the request is sent as `POST` with multipart form-data (required for file uploads).\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST {{apiUrl}}/products/:id` (with `_method: PATCH`)\n\n**Auth:** Bearer Token (`{{token}}`)\n\n**Path Parameters:**\n| Parameter | Description |\n|---|---|\n| id | The unique ID of the product to update. Use `{{product_id}}`. |\n\n**Body (form-data):**\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| _method | string | Yes | Must be `PATCH` or `PUT` for method spoofing |\n| desc | string | No | Updated product description |\n| status | string | No | Updated status: `active`, `inactive`, `draft` |\n| name | string | No | Updated product name |\n| price | number | No | Updated price |\n| stock | integer | No | Updated stock quantity |\n| image | file | No | New product image |\n| type_id | string | No | Updated product type ID |"
